heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_voi_che_do_dinh_duong\" >C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#O_giai_doan_ga_con_vua_tach_khoi_me\" >\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u00e0 con v\u1eeba t\u00e1ch kh\u1ecfi m\u1eb9\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#Doi_voi_ga_truong_thanh\" >\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_trong_cham_soc\" >C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_ve_huan_luyen\" >C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi v\u1ec1 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-nuoi-ga-cho\u2026o-nguoi-moi-choi\/\">C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi<\/a> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00ec \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">SV368<\/a> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ngay nh\u00e9.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_voi_che_do_dinh_duong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 nhanh l\u1edbn th\u00ec \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i cho \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c h\u1ea1t. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 ng\u0169 c\u1ed1c, l\u00faa, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t, \u2026 \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung cho g\u00e0 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9c \u0103n gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eb1n l\u1eb1n, giun \u0111\u1ea5t, d\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean chia b\u1eefa \u0103n cho g\u00e0 th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1eefa l\u00e0 9 gi\u1edd s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 5 gi\u1edd chi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed7i b\u1eefa cho g\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u1ea3ng 3\/4 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00e0 l\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7. \u1ede m\u1ed7i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"O_giai_doan_ga_con_vua_tach_khoi_me\"><\/span><b>\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u00e0 con v\u1eeba t\u00e1ch kh\u1ecfi m\u1eb9\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y th\u00ec ngo\u00e0i b\u1eefa \u0103n ch\u00ednh n\u00ean cho ch\u00fang \u0103n t\u1ef1 do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1ee9c \u0103n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap g\u00e0 t\u1eadp t\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfm \u0103n v\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3177\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3177\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3177 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-8.jpg\" alt=\"T\u00f9y m\u1ed7i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0103n kh\u00e1c nhau\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-8.jpg?v=1709294274 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-8-300x150.jpg?v=1709294274 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-8-768x384.jpg?v=1709294274 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3177\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00f9y m\u1ed7i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0103n kh\u00e1c nhau<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi_voi_ga_truong_thanh\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh\u00a0 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n cho g\u00e0 \u0103n th\u00eam chu\u1ed1i, th\u1ecbt b\u00f2 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e0 chua, l\u01b0\u01a1n, \u2026 B\u1eefa ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00f3c v\u00e0 ng\u00f4. Bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n cho g\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u0103n th\u00eam rau xanh. M\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i th\u00ec cho \u0103n th\u00eam th\u00f3c v\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> trong ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n cho g\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng th\u00eam thu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m vitamin B v\u00e0o m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n. N\u00ean cho g\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 vi\u00ean thu\u1ed1c m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, cho g\u00e0 \u0103n th\u00eam v\u00e0i t\u00e9p t\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, tr\u00e1nh gi\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3178\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3178\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3178 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-8.jpg\" alt=\"G\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nhi\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-8.jpg?v=1709294275 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-8-300x150.jpg?v=1709294275 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-8-768x384.jpg?v=1709294275 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3178\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nhi\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_trong_cham_soc\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c. G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u00fat v\u1ebb b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u01a1i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft t\u1ec9a l\u00f4ng n\u00e1ch, c\u1ed5, h\u1eadu m\u00f4n, \u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ebd m\u1ecdc l\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhanh. Do \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ec9a l\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho g\u00e0. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n t\u1ec9a l\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u00f4i ngh\u1ec7, ph\u00e8n chua v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1i, \u0111i k\u00e8m l\u00e0 ng\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u l\u00ean th\u00e2n g\u00e0. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00f4ng g\u00e0 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn, Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi gian th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 4 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1ec7 sinh, t\u1eafm cho g\u00e0. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, sau khi v\u1ec7 sinh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o l\u00f4ng r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi b\u00f4i ngh\u1ec7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3179\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3179\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3179 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-8.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-8.jpg?v=1709294276 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-8-300x150.jpg?v=1709294276 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-8-768x384.jpg?v=1709294276 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3179\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_nuoi_ga_choi_cho_nguoi_moi_choi_ve_huan_luyen\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi v\u1ec1 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong<\/span><b> c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">v\u1ec1 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n cho g\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n g\u00e0 s\u00e1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Trong c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi <\/b>v\u1edbi ch\u0103m nu\u00f4i g\u00e0, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean nh\u1ed1t g\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do, linh ho\u1ea1t. Qua \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u01a1 b\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho g\u00e0. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1y cho g\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch ra \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi g\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd quen d\u1ea7n. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n n\u00ean cho g\u00e0 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quen v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3180\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3180\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3180 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-4.jpg\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-4.jpg?v=1709294276 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-4-300x150.jpg?v=1709294276 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-4-768x384.jpg?v=1709294276 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3180\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Hi v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb SV368 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean v\u00e0o g\u00e0 ngay h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00ec \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3177,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[88],"class_list":["post-2527","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc","tag-cach-nuoi-ga-choi-cho-nguoi-moi-choi"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2527","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2527"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2527\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5838,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2527\/revisions\/5838"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3177"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2527"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2527"},{"tax